msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.2.11"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.2.12"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no "
"offense."

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Departing without informing of the proper building procedure"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.7.3.3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1542"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.2"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.3"
msgid "Na ca samādisati—"
msgstr "but he does not tell them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.4"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"to build it on a site which has been approved, where no harm will be done, "
"and which has a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.5"
msgid ""
"Tassa vihāraṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti "
"saṃghādisesena dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If they build a dwelling whose site has not been approved, where harm will "
"be done, and which lacks a space on all sides, he commits one offense "
"entailing suspension and two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.6"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
