"one offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.8"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="32"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1543"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.9"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.10"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.11"
msgid "Na ca samādisati—"
msgstr "but he does not tell them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.12"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and "
"which has a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.13"
msgid ""
"Tassa vihāraṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti "
"dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If they build a dwelling whose site has been approved, where harm will be "
"done, and which lacks a space on all sides, he commits two offenses of wrong "
"conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.14"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one "
"offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.15"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.3.16"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no "
"offense."

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Departing and then hearing about wrong building procedure"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.7.3.4"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1544"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.2"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.3"
msgid "Samādisati ca—"
msgstr "He tells them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.4"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and "
"which has a space on all sides,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.5"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"but they build one whose site has not been approved, where harm will be "
"done, and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.6"
msgid ""
"So suṇāti—“vihāro kira me kayirati adesi­ta­vatthuko sārambho "
"aparikkamano”ti."
msgstr "If he hears about it,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.7"
msgid "Tena bhikkhunā sāmaṃ vā gantabbaṃ dūto vā pāhetabbo—"
msgstr ""
"he must either go there himself or send a message, and he must tell them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.8"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and "
"which has a space on all sides. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.9"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho cā”ti … pe …"
msgstr "whose site has been approved, and where no harm will be done. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.10"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu saparikkamano cā”ti … pe …"
msgstr "whose site has been approved, and which has a space on all sides. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.11"
msgid "“desitavatthuko hotū”ti."
msgstr "whose site has been approved."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.12"
msgid "No ce sāmaṃ vā gaccheyya dūtaṃ vā pahiṇeyya, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he neither goes himself nor sends a message, he commits an offense of "
"wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="34"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1545"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.13"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.14"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.15"
msgid "Samādisati ca—"
msgstr "He tells them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.16"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and "
"which has a space on all sides,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.17"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"but they build one whose site has been approved, where harm will be done, "
"and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.18"
msgid ""
"So suṇāti—“vihāro kira me kayirati desitavatthuko sārambho aparikkamano”ti."
msgstr "If he hears about it,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.19"
msgid "Tena bhikkhunā sāmaṃ vā gantabbaṃ dūto vā pāhetabbo—"
msgstr ""
"he must either go there himself or send a message, and he must tell them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.20"
msgid "“anārambho ca hotu saparikkamano cā”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"to build one where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides. "
"… <span class=\"pe\">This paragraph is to be expanded as in <a class=\"cr\" "
"href=\"./pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6#64\">Saṅghādisesa 6, paragraphs 64–75</a>.</span> …"

#. The last two sets of ellipses points are not found in MS. I have added them for clarification.
#. VAR: hotū”ti → hotūti … pe … anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ (bj) | hotūti … pe … (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.21"
msgid "“anārambho hotū”ti."
msgstr "where no harm will be done. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.22"
msgid "“Saparikkamano hotū”ti,"
msgstr "which has a space on all sides. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.4.23"
msgid "anāpatti."
msgstr "There is no offense."

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Offenses for appointed builders"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="35"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.7.3.5"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1546"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.2"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.3"
msgid "Samādisati ca—"
msgstr "He tells them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.4"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and "
"which has a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.5"
msgid ""
"Tassa vihāraṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti "
"kārukānaṃ tiṇṇaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If they build one whose site has not been approved, where harm will be done, "
"and which lacks a space on all sides, the builders commit three offenses of "
"wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.6"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, the builders "
"commit two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.7"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, the "
"builders commit two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.8"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, the builders "
"commit one offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="36"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1547"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.9"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.10"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.11"
msgid "Samādisati ca—"
msgstr "He tells them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.12"
msgid "“desitavatthuko ca hotu anārambho ca saparikkamano cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"to build one whose site has been approved, where no harm will be done, and "
"which has a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.13"
msgid ""
"Tassa vihāraṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti "
"kārukānaṃ dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If they build one whose site has been approved, where harm will be done, and "
"which lacks a space on all sides, the builders commit two offenses of wrong "
"conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.14"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, the builders "
"commit one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.15"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti kārukānaṃ dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, the "
"builders commit one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.5.16"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no "
"offense."

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Unfinished when he returns"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="37"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.7.3.6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1548"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.2"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.270"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.3"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They build one whose site has not been approved, where harm will be done, "
"and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.4"
msgid ""
"So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā so vihāro aññassa vā dātabbo "
"bhinditvā vā puna kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"If it is unfinished when he returns, that dwelling is to be given to someone "
"else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.5"
msgid ""
"No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti saṃghādisesena "
"dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, "
"he commits one offense entailing suspension and two offenses of wrong "
"conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.6"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one "
"offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.7"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.8"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="38"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1549"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.9"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.10"
msgid "“vihāraṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a dwelling and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.11"
msgid "Tassa vihāraṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They build one whose site has been approved, where harm will be done, and "
"which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.12"
msgid ""
"So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā so vihāro aññassa vā dātabbo "
"bhinditvā vā puna kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"If it is unfinished when he returns, that dwelling is to be given to someone "
"else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.13"
msgid ""
"No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti dvinnaṃ "
"dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, "
"he commits two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.14"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one "
"offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.15"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.6.16"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no "
"offense."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations part 2"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.7.3.7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1550"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.1"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he finishes what he began himself, he commits an offense entailing "
"suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="40"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1551"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.2"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he gets others to finish what he began himself, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="41"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1552"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.3"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he finishes himself what was begun by others, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1553"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.4"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he gets others to finish what was begun by others, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.4a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="43"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1554"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.5"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.6"
msgid "leṇe guhāya tiṇakuṭikāya"
msgstr "if it is a shelter, if it is a cave, if it is a grass hut;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.7"
msgid "aññassatthāya vāsāgāraṃ ṭhapetvā"
msgstr "if it is built for someone else;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.8"
msgid "sabbattha."
msgstr "if it is anything apart from a dwelling;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.9"
msgid "Anāpatti ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.10"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="44"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1555"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss7:pts-cs3.7.11"
msgid "Vihāra­kāra­sikkhā­padaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr "The seventh rule, the training rule on building dwellings, is finished."

